{"tid":1726292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"整體上我覺得呢個禮拜局部癱瘓香港幾成功","createTime":"2019-11-16T05:48:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T06:24:45.000Z","uid":73972,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"17259064ef81127dd452c6bc9a20563d6118d01a","tid":1726292,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:48:58.000Z","msg":"1）叫做第一個突破，好好既學習，做得唔好既應該檢討反思改進<br />\n<br />\n2）行動升級左，運動持續進行中，無變到死氣沈沈，無係沈默中滅亡<br />\n<br />\n3）將運動升級慢慢潛移默化入港豬各個階層，令佢地慢慢適應運動，逼佢地參與其中同表態（無論支持定反對），無人可以置身事外<br />\n<br />\n4）世界各地領袖有反應，打嘴炮又好，有行動又好，將香港情況繼續暴露係世界目光<br />\n<br />\n5）中大撒退係好好既示威模範展現，有進有退，緊守be water理念"},{"pid":"7447b890b2985a3f77946d044f68632b54090d0e","tid":1726292,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:10:54.000Z","msg":"罷工返工都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 輕輕鬆鬆又一星期"},{"pid":"22a07a5180e1f729dc2ca3ab3c95711577a00ae9","tid":1726292,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:11:09.000Z","msg":"［區選］藍絲散水運動，正式開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1726325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1726325</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1ad79d511dc65a635ffb2dfbba8fe58f8c78e022","tid":1726292,"uid":132729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799ea66ecee4c09986adb528a145816a3b985ab8","tid":1726292,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:14:58.000Z","msg":"一直揾唔到藉口罷工既市民表示高興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d449f30eed28f5c43fee8ebb9cea639486623f15","tid":1726292,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:15:45.000Z","msg":"[和理塞] 連續塞足五日嘅體會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ewQhqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ewQhqS</a>"},{"pid":"d8db9b2d404c241